name: Doctor Who Quotes Project
description: 12 Quotes from Doctor Who to celebrate 50 years. These are high quality digital prints on UK A5 sized heavy weight card stock. A LIMITED EDITION SET There are 12 cards in the set and there will only be 50 sets for sale, once they are gone the set will not be reprinted. There are 11 quotes from the TV incarnations of the doctor and 1 bonus card with a quote from the 8th Doctor's Big Finish audio adventures. You can find out more about the series on my website's DW Quotes section
